data.description: *Buyer financing fell through* A First-Time Homebuyer's dream! Low maintenance and no yard work! On top of that, this home has been renovated to include LVP flooring throughout, a walk-in shower in the Primary Bathroom, a smart thermostat and smart lighting downstairs. For your young professionals, the home is located close to I95 and I295 for quick commutes to work, and minutes away from the airport. For young parents, the home is walking distance to Biscayne Bay Leadership Academy. And for the summers off, there's a pool located at the front of the community and RiverCity Marketplace is a few minutes drive. Don't miss out on this updated end-unit gem with a nice sized lot!
